This paper deals with a problem in AI, specifically in reinforcement learning, and introduces a novel concept of "restraining bolt" inspired by science fiction. The paper also uses logical specifications in linear time logic on finite traces (LTLf/LDLf). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI, followed by cs.LG (machine learning), cs.RO (robotics), cs.SE (software engineering), and cs.SY (systems and control).
